<h3>III. Operatii aritmetice si conditii</h3>
<a href="cap2.html">Capitolul II</a> | <a href="cap3.html">Capitolul IV</a><br><br>
Dupa cum s-ar outea sa stii, in JavaScript ai la indemana diverse operatii aritmetice.<br>
Acestea sunt facute cu autorul operatorilor si operanzilor.<br>
Luand ca exemplu: 2 + 2 = 4; + este operator; 2 si 2 sunt operanzi; 4 este rezultatul.<br>
Operanzii pot fi variabile sau numere, booleeni, mesaje etc.<br>
Comparatie intre operatorii din mate si cei din JavaScript:<br><code>
mate -&gt; javascript<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;+&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;+<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;-<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;x&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;*<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;/<br></code>
<br>
Al doilea lucru despre care vom discuta in acest capitol sunt operatiile conditionate. Acestea vor aparea folositoare in multe cazuri.<br>
Operatiile conditionate ne ajuta atunci cand trebuie sa executam un set de instructiuni daca o anumita conditie e respectata(adevarata) sau, in cazul in care conditia e  falsa, sa executam alt set de instructiuni.<br>
Acestea se rezolva cu autorul instructiunii <code>if</code>(in engleza: daca).<br>
Sintaxa instructiunii <code>if</code>(cum se foloseste):<br>
<code>if(conditie){<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Instructiuni_adevarat<br>
}</code><br>
Daca e nevoie se poate adauga <code>else</code>:<br>
<code>if(conditie){<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Instructiuni_adevarat<br>
}else{<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Instructiuni_fals<br>
}</code><br>
In cazul in care conditia este respectata/este adevarata, se vor executa <code>Instructiuni_adevarat</code>. Altfel, daca sunt specificate, se vor executa <code>Instructiuni_fals</code>.<br>
Conditiile sunt formate tot din operatori si operanzi, insa de data asta operatorii sunt 'mai mare', 'mai mic sau egal', 'mai mic' etc.<br>
Operatori:<br><code>
mate -&gt; javascript<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&ge;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;=<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&le;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;=<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;== sau ===<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&ne;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;!= sau !==<br></code>
<br>
Exemple de conditii:<br>
<code>2 + 2 &gt;= 4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ADEVARAT<br>
2 + 2 == 4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ADEVARAT<br>
6 * 5 &gt;= 3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ADEVARAT<br>
6 + 9 &lt; 5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FALS<br></code>

